"1.Turn on / off the debug of the modem log, the default is on

 2.Log types are logcat log, event log, radio log, kernel log and input log;

 3.Log storage path is data/log/wt_logs;

 4.Can set a single log file size, select the log file size: 8M, 12M, 16M, the default is 8M

 5.Other Android log also have factory and charger, the default is always open;

 6.The factory logs path is /cache/factory_logs;

 7.The charger logs path is /cache/charger_logs;

 8.The data partition before encryption of log path is /cache/wt_logs;

 9.Delete the log will delete old wtlog, and clear the cache of logcat.

 Note: Each project factory and charger logs and cache wtlog is not necessarily, please prevail in the actual situation."

"1.Turn on / off the debug of the modem log, the default is off

 2.Log types are logcat log, event log and radio log;

 3.Log storage path is sdcard/wt_logs/ap_logs;

 4.Can set a single log file size or counts, select the log file size: 8M, 12M, 16M, the default is 8M;select the log file counts: 10, 20, 30, the default is 10;

