"1.Turn on / off the debug of the modem log, the default is off;

 2.Log storage path is sdcard/diag_logs;

 3.Can be set to start the next boot modem log crawl;

 4.Can set the modem log policy, file size, the number of files and delete the old log file, but need to close the log switch"

"5.According to different test requirements, change the modem log policy file, the default protocol related 1）Audio related(audio.cfg) 2）Protocol related(modem.cfg) 3）Sensor related(sensor.cfg) 4）Wlan, GPS and Bluetooth related(wcn.cfg)
6.According to different needs, you can change the size of the modem log file, selectable items are: 50M, 100M, 200M, the default item is 100M;
7.According to different needs, you can change the number of modem log files, selectable items are: 10,20,50, the default item is 10"

"1.The log storage path is data/log/tcp_logs;

 2.You can set the next boot whether to start the log crawl;

 3.Packet capture process is required to test the application to access the network;

 4.Crawl the log file suffix with time;

 5.Can save up 6 log files;

 6.Can enter the log package, export TcpDump log file.;"

"1.Can choose to package to the memory device or external memory device, the default for the memory device;

 2.Check the type of log need to package the package (Android log, ANR log, Dropbox log, bugreport log, etc.), by default, all checked, all unchecked, no log package;

 3.Select the finished click on the log package button after the pop-up prompt box, click OK will be selected after the log compression package to the built-in storage or external storage (depending on the default storage location), log_ current time named folder is The package of the log"

"4.Modem log file is too large, it is not unified for packaging, Modem log storage pathsdcard/diag_logs;

 5.When the log file is very long, the packaging process takes some time, please be patient waiting for the package to complete;

 6.It is recommended that the mobile phone every time after a period of time, empty the Android log, and then open the switch, you can keep the new log, can also reduce the time spent packaging and uploading;

 7.If stay long time in the packaged state, such as packaging keys for a long time for the gray state, please restart the phone and try again."

"1.Each time a package is completed, a record is generated;

 2.Click one of them to access the details interface;

 3.Long press a certain item, you can enter the editing interface, you can select all and delete;

 4.You need to fill out the form information before uploading the log, otherwise you will not be able to upload it;

 5.Do not add too many attachments, because the file is too large will affect the upload efficiency;"

"6.Upload function need to connect to the data network or wlan;

 7.If upload fails occurs, while waiting for a stable network before uploading;

 8. Please try not to upload more than 200M file, the network is unstable, the upload process may fail, if still can not upload, use adb or mtp connect PC-side export log;

 9. If stay long time in the upload state, there can not be re-uploaded for a long time, please restart the phone and try again."

